data.description: Motivated seller,  Gorgeous 4 bedroom home, Move in ready includes Stainless steel appliances/ washer and dryer. Large open kitchen with granite countertop and corner walk in pantry. Separate dining all flows to living room which is great for entertainment. Primary room with separate shower and tub, walk in closet, Beautiful covered patio. Residents of Goose Creek Reserve enjoy a swimming pool, playground, and walking trails. only minutes away from dining, shopping, and entertainment at Baytown Town Square.
